/GsimDetector/world/box/air/inz1/setOuterMaterial G4_AIR
/GsimDetector/world/box/air/inz1/setSensitiveDetectorWithName in 5

/GsimDetectorFactory/GsimBox/buildAndRegister inx0 /world/box/air +15*cm-1*0.5*mm 0 0 0 0 0 
